titles.title: An original resolution to authorize the printing of a collection of the rules of the committees of the Senate.

calendar.text: Committee on Rules ordered to be reported an original measure.

action.text: Committee on Rules. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Ford. Without written report.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 2/18/1993--Introduced. Directs that a collection of the rules of the committees of the Senate be printed as a Senate document. Provides for 600 additional copies of such document for the Committee on Rules and Administration.
